TopicTitle: KSP stops loading after being launched

Articles.Content:
Ksp stops loading after being launched only after about 15 seconds. I do indeed have about 60 mods installed but up until now they haven't been a problem. 

Here is the KSP.log: https://share.multcloud.link/share/7211a1f5-dc40-413a-8acb-845a6f0d1503

8 hours ago, Matisse08 said:

Ksp stops loading after being launched only after about 15 seconds. I do indeed have about 60 mods installed but up until now they haven't been a problem. 

Here is the KSP.log: https://share.multcloud.link/share/7211a1f5-dc40-413a-8acb-845a6f0d1503

This is installed incorrectly: 

[LOG 17:06:25.692] AssemblyLoader: Loading assembly at /Applications/KSP_osx/GameData/CryoEngines_2_0_6/B9PartSwitch/Plugins/B9PartSwitch.dll

You have an incompatible mod installed somewhere:

[EXC 17:06:52.978] MissingFieldException: Field 'KSPParticleEmitter.pe' not found.

I'd really suggest using CKAN to prevent these issues.
